{"tid":1491868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生如果定期罷課運動成功推展，會係對政權嘅一大打擊。請密切關注。","createTime":"2019-08-20T14:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:27:02.000Z","uid":294955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdff52575465c642b247e7fc465c3235f181d1b","tid":1491868,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"街頭抗爭只係製造聲勢，已達到目的，就係全世界都關注香港。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我覺得<span style=\"color: gold;\">衝擊政權體制</span>先係主菜，你諗，教育局反對罷課，擔心嘅唔通真係學生嘅安全同埋福祉嗎，定係學生對政權嘅起義挑戰？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果大量學生自發付代價定期罷課成功，我相信其他好多衝擊政權體制嘅起義行動會陸續有來。而呢個就先<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">真正係時代革命嘅開始</span></span>。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請考慮如何擴大整場運動嘅抗爭戰線同手段，唔好再拘泥於set deadline。你冇bargaining power去定deadline有咩作用？<br />\n<br />\n真正bargaining甚至唔係幾百萬人出嚟遊行或者有幾多人做前線勇武抗爭（雖然都有其重要性）, 而係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">更多香港人願意將革命精神注入生活，人人抗爭，無分彼此</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n主佑香港。"},{"pid":"1af6021b54692660b06534844f2d5eb6920bf536","tid":1491868,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b3a6a86482ff38c112ad264cf8dfa06fa328710","tid":1491868,"uid":9619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"支持罷課！"},{"pid":"df7107ebcd19fa2f914ed15f14177c140746fc68","tid":1491868,"uid":116608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"[罷課準備] 老師家長大學生入晒黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491660</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e65c4b5ca06e2432a88f4923046efc5972767f9","tid":1491868,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"同意！！！<br />\n<br />\n８２３人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-a